          "a": "Visually inventory equipment; account for keying material; page-check publications; both sign."
        },
        {
          "q": "CMS 1 defines",
          "a": "Minimum requirements for COMSEC inventory."
        },
        {
          "q": "Are erasures allowed in logs?",
          "a": "No."
        },
        {
